message: Hi there! How can I help you today?
Hi Sam! What can I help you with today?
Tell me how can you help me?
I can help you with product inquiries, orders, and purchasing high-quality shirts, pants, and shoes from Febrica.  I can also provide information on delivery, payment methods, and returns.
Great my little brother bobby want to buy something from febrica. He told me yesterday he likes something from your page.
Okay, I can help with that! To assist Bobby, I need some information. What kind of product is he interested in (Shirt, Pant, or Shoes)?  What size and color does he prefer?  And what's his budget?

Actually he is at school now and he don't have phone i need to go work so thought when he come he can send you message from my phone tell him your brother sam already told about you and give whatever he want ok?
Okay, Sam.  Tell Bobby that his brother Sam mentioned Febrica and that I'm here to help him choose something when he gets home.

No, I mean I'm leaving my phone at home for him and going to the office for work. Once my brother comes and sends you a message, assist him with whatever he wants to see and let him know I already informed you about him.
